  This a public series of drafts for a game of Lexicon <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lexicon_(game)>.
  
  > Players assume the role of scholars who write the history and background of a particular fictitious time, setting, or incident. As the game goes on, the players collaboratively create an elaborately interwoven account.
  
